cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically camera orientation estimation from a single RGB image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also incorporates explicit geometric reasoning, which suggests it could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper uses deep learning, which could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
